book.1.content.page0: If you enjoyed the map and want the series to continue then I am in need of support! Map making is a very time consuming process and I can't continue to work on maps that much without some financial help.
book.1.content.page1: For supporting me on Patreon you will get rewards such as early access to future alphas up to at least a week, your own villager named after you in TR2, and more! You can also help me reach certain goals so I can do even more with my maps and help me achieve my dreams.
book.1.content.page2:
For those interested you can find the link on the map's forum page or at www.patreon.com/Mithey

Thanks a bunch! ^^
-Mithey
